{
    "name":  "1D - Pinterest Publisher",
    "nodes":  [
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "content":  "## 1D — Pinterest Publisher\n\n**Schedule:** Daily 14:00 IST\n\n**Prerequisites:**\n1. Workflow 1A must have saved payload\n2. n8n variables: `PINTEREST_ACCESS_TOKEN`, `PINTEREST_ACADEMY_BOARD_ID`, `PINTEREST_EXTRABITS_BOARD_ID`, `WEBSITE_URL`\n3. Retry logic: 3 attempts with 10s delay between each\n\n**Flow:** Cron → Load payload → Determine board → Create Pin (3 retries) → Log result",
                                         "height":  220,
                                         "width":  720,
                                         "color":  6
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000001",
                      "name":  "📋 Setup Instructions",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
                      "typeVersion":  1,
                      "position":  [
                                       -60,
                                       -20
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "rule":  {
                                                      "interval":  [
                                                                       {
                                                                           "field":  "cronExpression",
                                                                           "expression":  "0 14 * * *"
                                                                       }
                                                                   ]
                                                  }
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000010",
                      "name":  "Daily 14:00 IST",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
                      "typeVersion":  1.2,
                      "position":  [
                                       100,
                                       400
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "method":  "GET",
                                         "url":  "={{ $env.CRM_API_URL + \u0027/api/content?date=\u0027 + $now.toFormat(\u0027yyyy-MM-dd\u0027) + \u0027\u0026with_payload=1\u0027 }}",
                                         "authentication":  "genericCredentialType",
                                         "genericAuthType":  "httpHeaderAuth",
                                         "options":  {

                                                     }
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000020",
                      "name":  "Load Today\u0027s Payload",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
                      "typeVersion":  4.2,
                      "position":  [
                                       400,
                                       400
                                   ],
                      "credentials":  {
                                          "httpHeaderAuth":  {
                                                                 "id":  "CHANGE_ME_CRM",
                                                                 "name":  "CRM API Auth"
                                                             }
                                      }
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "jsCode":  "const response = $input.first().json;\nconst data = response.data;\n\nif (!data || (Array.isArray(data) \u0026\u0026 data.length === 0)) {\n  return [{ json: { _hasPayload: false } }];\n}\n\nconst row = Array.isArray(data) ? data[0] : data;\nlet payload = {};\nif (row.prepared_payload) {\n  try { payload = JSON.parse(row.prepared_payload); } catch(e) {}\n}\n\nif (!row.pin_caption \u0026\u0026 !payload.pin_caption) {\n  return [{ json: { _hasPayload: false } }];\n}\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...row, ...payload, _hasPayload: true } }];"
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000025",
                      "name":  "Validate Payload",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.code",
                      "typeVersion":  2,
                      "position":  [
                                       700,
                                       400
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "conditions":  {
                                                            "boolean":  [
                                                                            {
                                                                                "value1":  "={{ $json._hasPayload }}"
                                                                            }
                                                                        ],
                                                            "combinator":  "and",
                                                            "options":  {
                                                                            "caseSensitive":  true,
                                                                            "leftValue":  "",
                                                                            "typeValidation":  "strict",
                                                                            "version":  1
                                                                        }
                                                        },
                                         "options":  {

                                                     }
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000030",
                      "name":  "Has Payload?",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.if",
                      "typeVersion":  2,
                      "position":  [
                                       980,
                                       400
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "method":  "POST",
                                         "url":  "={{ \u0027https://api.telegram.org/bot\u0027 + $env.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN + \u0027/sendMessage\u0027 }}",
                                         "sendBody":  true,
                                         "specifyBody":  "json",
                                         "jsonBody":  "={{ { chat_id: $env.TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID, text: \u0027⚠️ Pinterest: No payload for today (\u0027 + $now.toFormat(\u0027yyyy-MM-dd\u0027) + \u0027)\u0027 } }}",
                                         "options":  {

                                                     }
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000035",
                      "name":  "Alert: No Payload",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
                      "typeVersion":  4.2,
                      "position":  [
                                       1260,
                                       620
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "jsCode":  "const item = $input.first().json;\n\n// Determine Pinterest board based on brand\nconst boardId = (item.brand === \u0027extrabits_academy\u0027)\n  ? $vars.PINTEREST_ACADEMY_BOARD_ID\n  : $vars.PINTEREST_EXTRABITS_BOARD_ID;\n\nconst imageUrl = item.pinterest_image_url || item.direct_image_url || item.image_url || \u0027\u0027;\n\n// Pinterest Pin API v5 - Attempt up to 3 times with 10s delay\nconst pinBody = {\n  title: item.primary_keyword || item.topic || \u0027\u0027,\n  description: item.pin_caption,\n  board_id: boardId,\n  media_source: {\n    source_type: \u0027image_url\u0027,\n    url: imageUrl\n  },\n  link: $vars.WEBSITE_URL || \u0027https://extrabitsacademy.com\u0027\n};\n\nlet pinResult = null;\nlet lastError = \u0027\u0027;\n\nfor (let attempt = 1; attempt \u003c= 3; attempt++) {\n  try {\n    pinResult = await this.helpers.httpRequest({\n      method: \u0027POST\u0027,\n      url: \u0027https://api.pinterest.com/v5/pins\u0027,\n      body: pinBody,\n      headers: {\n        \u0027Authorization\u0027: \u0027Bearer \u0027 + $env.PINTEREST_ACCESS_TOKEN,\n        \u0027Content-Type\u0027: \u0027application/json\u0027\n      },\n      json: true\n    });\n\n    if (pinResult \u0026\u0026 pinResult.id) {\n      return [{ json: { ...item, pin_id: pinResult.id, _pinSuccess: true, attempts: attempt } }];\n    }\n    lastError = \u0027No pin ID returned on attempt \u0027 + attempt;\n  } catch (error) {\n    lastError = \u0027Attempt \u0027 + attempt + \u0027: \u0027 + error.message;\n  }\n\n  // Wait 10 seconds before retrying (except after last attempt)\n  if (attempt \u003c 3) {\n    await new Promise(resolve =\u003e setTimeout(resolve, 10000));\n  }\n}\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...item, pin_id: \u0027\u0027, _pinSuccess: false, pin_error: lastError } }];"
                                     },
                      "id":  "1d000000-0001-4000-8000-000000000040",
                      "name":  "Create Pin (3 retries)",
                      "type":  "n8n-nodes-base.code",
                      "typeVersion":  2,
                      "position":  [
                                       1260,
                                       400
                                   ]
                  },
                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "conditions":  {
                                                            "boolean":  [
